| Chinese Yuan | `CNY` | CN¥ | 2 | CN¥10.00 |
| Philippine Peso | `PHP` | ₱ | 2 | ₱10.00 |
| Indian Rupee | `INR` | ₹ | 2 | ₹10.00 |
